definitions.definition: Ellipsis of Blandford Forum : a market town and civil parish with a town council in Dorset , England , previously in North Dorset district ( OS grid ref ST8806 ) .
A community in Chester district municipality, Nova Scotia , Canada .
A community and former township in Blandford-Blenheim township, Oxford County , Ontario , Canada .
A town and census-designated place therein, in Hampden County , Massachusetts , United States .
A former town annexed by Petersburg , Virginia , United States .
A village in Upper Hunter Shire, New South Wales , Australia .
